        <title>初夏轻染九寨沟，万顷琉璃映翠微</title>
        <link>https://majiao2.github.io/2025/%E5%88%9D%E5%A4%8F%E8%BD%BB%E6%9F%93%E4%B9%9D%E5%AF%A8%E6%B2%9F%E4%B8%87%E9%A1%B7%E7%90%89%E7%92%83%E6%98%A0%E7%BF%A0%E5%BE%AE/</link>
